<br>
Cause? Unknown. Treatment? They can only treat the symptoms, which means I take a dieretic which lowers the amount of fluid overall in my body, and vicoden for the pain from the headaches. The fluid levels aren't constant, they flucuate. So some days it's fine, other days it hurts like shit.<br>
<br>
