<br>
I was researching every possibility....guess what also works for PTC? Marijuana. There are several cases out there where PTC completely resolved, because marijuana lowers the CSF pressure.<br>
<br>
And as many of you also know, my husband is a police officer. <br>
<br>
/sigh<br>
<br>
